title: Runaways 11 (2009) (Minutemen-DTs)
description:
Runaways 11 (2009) (Minutemen-DTs)
by Kathryn Immonen, Sara Pichelli, David Lafuente

New creative team! Cataclysmic new direction! In this arc, one Runaway will die, and one Runaway will live! Rising star Kathryn Immonen (PATSY WALKER: HELLCAT) and Sarah Pichelli (NYX) take the reins of the Runaways. Making out? Check. Cliffhangers? Check. Silly hats? Check. This is the Runaways arc you CAN'T miss.
